<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UPITI Employees Association</title>
    <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <header class="bg-white shadow-md border-b-4 border-blue-700 w-full">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-4 md:mb-0">
                <img src="logo.png" alt="UPITI Logo" class="h-32 w-auto object-contain">
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center flex-1 px-4">
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl text-red-600 font-bold mb-2">उत्तर प्रदेश औद्योगिक प्रशिक्षण संस्थान कर्मचारी संघ</h1>
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-blue-400 mb-1">UTTAR Pradesh Industrial Training Institute Employees Association.</h2>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">सम्बद्ध: राज्य कर्मचारी संयुक्त परिषद, उत्तर प्रदेश</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-4 md:mt-0">
                <img src="logo2.png" alt="Second Logo" class="h-32 w-auto object-contain">
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="bg-blue-800 text-white shadow-lg sticky top-0 z-50 w-full">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center space-x-2 md:space-x-6 py-3 text-sm md:text-base font-medium">
                <li><a href="#" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">मुख्य पृष्ठ</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">हमारे बारे में</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">संगठन संरचना</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">घटनाक्रम</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">गैलरी</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">शासनादेश / आदेश</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">सम्पर्क सूत्र</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 my-8">
        <div x-data="{ activeSlide: 1 }" 
             x-init="setInterval(() => { activeSlide = activeSlide === 5 ? 1 : activeSlide + 1 }, 5000)" 
             class="relative w-full overflow-hidden shadow-lg rounded-xl">
            
            <div class="relative w-full aspect-[21/6]">
                <div x-show="activeSlide === 1" x-transition.opacity.duration.1000ms class="absolute inset-0"><img src="slide-1.jpg" alt="1" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                <div x-show="activeSlide === 2" x-transition.opacity.duration.1000ms class="absolute inset-0"><img src="slide-2.jpg" alt="2" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                <div x-show="activeSlide === 3" x-transition.opacity.duration.1000ms class="absolute inset-0"><img src="slide-3.jpg" alt="3" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                <div x-show="activeSlide === 4" x-transition.opacity.duration.1000ms class="absolute inset-0"><img src="slide-4.jpg" alt="4" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                <div x-show="activeSlide === 5" x-transition.opacity.duration.1000ms class="absolute inset-0"><img src="slide-5.jpg" alt="5" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 w-full">
        <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 space-y-8">
            <section class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow border border-gray-200">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4 border-b-2 border-red-500 pb-2 inline-block">परिचय (Introduction)</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">उत्तर प्रदेश औद्योगिक प्रशिक्षण संस्थान कर्मचारी संघ में आपका स्वागत है। यह संगठन कर्मचारियों के हितों और अधिकारों की रक्षा के लिए समर्पित है...</p>
            </section>
        </div>

        <aside class="w-full md:w-1/3 space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow border border-gray-200 border-t-4 border-t-red-600">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-bell text-red-600 mr-2"></i> नवीन सूचानाएं</h3>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 h-64 overflow-y-auto rounded shadow-inner">
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-blue-800 font-medium">
                        <li>नवीनतम बैठक और निर्णय की जानकारी।</li>
                        <li>कर्मचारी कल्याण से जुड़ी नई सूचनाएं।</li>
                        <li>आगामी कार्यक्रमों की रूपरेखा।</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 py-8 border-t-4 border-blue-700 mt-auto w-full">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2026 UTTAR Pradesh Industrial Training Institute Employees Association.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
